high_descs: Turn around and go to the toilet.
Grab the spray bottle on the left that is on the back of the toilet.
Turn to the left and go to the metal rack.
Place the bottle on the top shelf of the metal rack.
Turn around and go back to the toilet.
Grab the spray bottle on the back of the toilet.
Turn around and go back to the metal shelf.
Place the spray bottle to the left of the bottle on the top shelf.
Turn around and face the toilet on your right.
Pick up a spray bottle from the toilet.
Turn around and walk to the metal shelves on your right.
Place the spray bottle on the shelf.
Walk back to the toilet.
Pick up a spray bottle from the toilet.
Walk back to the metal shelves.
Place the spray bottle on the shelf.
anns.task_desc: Place two spray bottles on a shelf.

high_descs: Turn left and walk up to the toilet
Pick up the left most blue spray bottle from the back of the toilet
Turn around and walk to the metal shelf in the opposite corner of the bathroom
Put the blue spray bottle on the top shelf
Turn around and walk across the room to the toilet
Pick up the blue spray bottle from the back of the toilet
Turn around and walk back across the room to the metal shelf
Put the spray bottle on the top shelf just to the right of the first blue bottle
anns.task_desc: Put the blue spray bottles on the metal shelf
